precis:
Enactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON
TERRITORY (2002, No. 7, FORTY MILE, FORT CUDAHY AND FORT CONSTANTINE
HISTORIC SITE, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits the staking of mineral claims or
prospecting in specific areas in the Yukon until October 1, 2008, and (b)
repeals the Prohibition of Entry on Certain Lands Order, No. 10 of 1997.
